  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Experience the thrilling adventures of George of the Jungle, a classic side-scrolling platformer reminiscent of Pitfall! As the fearless George, you'll navigate through a lush jungle environment, dodging hazards like mischievous monkeys and treacherous pits. Be careful, though - some obstacles can be deadly, so keep a sharp eye out for danger. But don't worry, George has got some tricks up his sleeve too! Swing from vines and collect precious eggs to boost your progress. Just remember to stay safe and have fun!",
      "lang": "en",
